(ns farsund.ui.core
  (:require [cljs.spec.alpha :as s]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [reagent.ratom :refer [make-reaction reaction]]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.timbre :as timbre]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]
            [oops.core :refer [oget ocall]]
            [mui.core :as mui]
            [mui.colors :as colors]
            [farsund.flex :as flex]
            [farsund.utils.core :as u]
            [farsund.utils.key :as key]
            [farsund.data.ui :as data.ui]
            [farsund.login.ui :as login.ui]
            [farsund.scanner.ui :as scanner.ui]

            ["@material-ui/icons/Add" :default AddIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Remove" :default RemoveIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Clear" :default ClearIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Search" :default SearchIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Menu" :default MenuIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/ChevronLeft" :default ChevronLeftIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Face" :default FaceIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Assignment" :default AssignmentIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Receipt" :default ReceiptIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Settings" :default SettingsIcon]))


(defn left-drawer-menu []
  (let [panel (rf/subscribe [:ui/panel])
        primary-color (rf/subscribe [:theme/get :palette :primary :main])]
    (fn []
      [flex/vbox
       [flex/hbox {:justify-content :flex-end}
        [mui/icon-button {:style    {:margin "0px"}
                          :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-left-drawer])}
         [:> ClearIcon]]]
       [mui/list
        [mui/list-item {:button         true
                        :disable-ripple true
                        :on-click       #(rf/dispatch [:ui/set-panel :eurocash-order])}
         [mui/list-item-icon {:style {:color (when (= :eurocash-order @panel) @primary-color)}}
          [:> AssignmentIcon]]
         [mui/list-item-text {:style {:white-space :nowrap}}
          "zamówienie eurocash"]]
        [mui/list-item {:button         true
                        :disable-ripple true
                        :on-click       #(rf/dispatch [:ui/set-panel :cg-order])}
         [mui/list-item-icon {:style {:color (when (= :cg-order @panel) @primary-color)}}
          [:> ReceiptIcon]]
         [mui/list-item-text {:style {:white-space :nowrap}}
          "zamówienie cg"]]
        [mui/list-item {:button         true
                        :disable-ripple true
                        :on-click       #(rf/dispatch [:ui/set-panel :settings])}
         [mui/list-item-icon {:style {:color (when (= :settings @panel) @primary-color)}}
          [:> SettingsIcon]]
         [mui/list-item-text
          "ustawienia"]]
        ]])))


(defn right-drawer-menu []
  (let [panel (rf/subscribe [:ui/panel])
        primary-color (rf/subscribe [:theme/get :palette :primary :main])
        gutter (rf/subscribe [:layout/gutter.px])
        parents-categories (rf/subscribe [:data/parent-categories])
        selected-categories (rf/subscribe [:data/selected-categories])
        min-margin (rf/subscribe [:data/min-margin])
        min-pace (rf/subscribe [:data/min-pace])
        pace-period (rf/subscribe [:data/pace-period])]
    (fn []
      [flex/vbox
       [flex/hbox {:justify-content :flex-end}
        [mui/icon-button {:style    {:margin "0px"}
                          :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-right-drawer])}
         [:> ClearIcon]]]
       [flex/scroller {:height "85vh"
                       :style  {:padding @gutter}}
        [flex/hbox {:height          48
                    :justify-content :center
                    :align-items     :center}
         [flex/box {:size 2}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body2} "kategorie"]]
         [flex/box {:size      1
                    :max-width "50%"}
          [mui/form-control
           [mui/select {:multiple     true
                        :value        @selected-categories
                        :input        (r/as-element [mui/input])
                        :render-value (fn [coll]
                                        (->> coll
                                             (map #(deref (rf/subscribe [:data/category-name %])))
                                             (str/join ", ")))
                        :on-change    #(rf/dispatch [:data/select-category (u/elem->val %)])
                        :MenuProps    {:PaperProps {:style {:max-height "75vh"}}}}
            (doall (for [[key value] @parents-categories]
                     [mui/menu-item {:key   key
                                     :value key}
                      [mui/checkbox {:checked @(rf/subscribe [:data/category-selected? key])}]
                      [mui/list-item-text {:primary value}]]))]]]]
        [flex/hbox {:height      48
                    :align-items :center}
         [flex/box {:size 3}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body1} "minimalna marża"]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/dec-min-margin])}
           [:> RemoveIcon]]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body1} (.toFixed @min-margin 2)]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/inc-min-margin])}
           [:> AddIcon]]]]
        [flex/hbox {:height      48
                    :align-items :center}
         [flex/box {:size 3}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body1} "minimalne tempo"]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/dec-min-pace])}
           [:> RemoveIcon]]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body1} (.toFixed @min-pace 2)]]
         [flex/box {:size            1
                    :justify-content :center}
          [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/inc-min-pace])}
           [:> AddIcon]]]]
        [flex/hbox {:height      48
                    :align-items :center}
         [flex/box {:size 1}
          [mui/typography {:variant :body2} "okres tempa"]]
         [flex/box {:size      1
                    :max-width "50%"}
          [mui/form-control {:style {:min-width "100%"}}
           [mui/select {:value        @pace-period
                        :input        (r/as-element [mui/input])
                        :render-value #(case %
                                         "day" "dzień"
                                         "weekday" "tydzień"
                                         "month" "miesiąc")
                        :on-change    #(rf/dispatch [:data/set-pace-period (u/elem->val %)])}
            [mui/menu-item {:value "day"}
             [mui/list-item-text {:primary "dzień"}]]
            [mui/menu-item {:value "weekday"}
             [mui/list-item-text {:primary "tydzień"}]]
            [mui/menu-item {:value "month"}
             [mui/list-item-text {:primary "miesiąc"}]]]]]]]
       [flex/hbox {:justify-content :space-between
                   :style           {:padding (str "0px " @gutter)}}
        [mui/button {:variant  :outlined
                     :color    :primary
                     :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:do
                                              [:data/make-market-order]
                                              [:ui/toggle-right-drawer]])}
         "generuj zamówienie"]
        [mui/button {:variant  :outlined
                     :color    :primary
                     :on-click #(rf/dispatch [:do
                                              [:data/generate-market-order]
                                              [:ui/toggle-right-drawer]])}
         "exportuj"]]])))


(defn search []
  (let [search-value (rf/subscribe [:data/tmp-search-value])]
    (fn []
      [mui/paper {:style {:height "42px"
                          :width  "100%"}}
       [mui/form-control {:full-width true}
        [mui/input {:default-value     (or @search-value "")
                    :disable-underline true
                    :end-adornment     (r/as-element
                                         [mui/input-adornment {:position :end}
                                          [mui/icon-button {:style {:margin "0px"}}
                                           [:> SearchIcon]]])
                    :on-change         (fn [e]
                                         (rf/dispatch [:data/set-tmp-search-value (u/elem->val e)]))
                    :on-key-press      (fn [e]
                                         (println :on-key-press (oget e :charCode))
                                         (key/on-enter
                                           e #(rf/dispatch [:data/set-search-value (u/elem->val e)])))
                    :style             {:padding    "4px 0px 4px 16px"
                                        :text-align :center}}]]])))


(defn app-bar []
  (let []
    (fn []
      [mui/app-bar {:position  :sticky
                    :elevation 2
                    :style     {:height "112px"}}
       [flex/box {:max-height "56px"}
        [mui/toolbar
         [flex/hbox {:size            1
                     :justify-content :space-between
                     :align-items     :center}
          [flex/box
           [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-left-drawer])}
            [:> MenuIcon]]]
          [flex/box
           [mui/typography {:variant :h5
                            :align   :center
                            ;:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/set-panel :warehouse])
                            }
            "farsund"]]
          [flex/box
           [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-right-drawer])}
            [:> SettingsIcon]]]]]]
       [flex/hbox {:justify-content :center}
        [flex/box {:size            "80%"
                   :justify-content :center}
         [search]]]])))





(defn mobile-page []
  (let [theme (rf/subscribe [:theme/get])
        panel (rf/subscribe [:ui/panel])
        left-drawer-open? (rf/subscribe [:ui/left-drawer-opened?])
        right-drawer-open? (rf/subscribe [:ui/right-drawer-opened?])]
    (fn []
      [mui/css-baseline
       [mui/mui-theme-provider {:theme @theme}
        [:<>
         ;drawers
         [mui/swipeable-drawer {:anchor     :left
                                :open       @left-drawer-open?
                                :on-open    #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-left-drawer])
                                :on-close   #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-left-drawer])
                                :variant    :temporary
                                :PaperProps {:style {:width "100vw"}}}
          [left-drawer-menu]]
         [mui/swipeable-drawer {:anchor     :right
                                :open       @right-drawer-open?
                                :on-open    #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-right-drawer])
                                :on-close   #(rf/dispatch [:ui/toggle-right-drawer])
                                :variant    :temporary
                                :PaperProps {:style {:width "100vw"}}}
          [right-drawer-menu]]
         ;dialogs
         ;[login/login-dialog]
         ;[register/register-dialog]
         [app-bar]
         [:div {:id    :main-view
                :style {:height "calc(100% - 112px)"}}
          (case @panel
            :eurocash-order [data.ui/mobile-page]
            ;:cg-order [scanner.ui/quagga-component]
            [:div "zabłądziłem"])]
         ]]])))


(defn main-page []
  (let [md? (rf/subscribe [:window/>=md?])]
    (fn []
      [mobile-page])))


(comment
  (second @(rf/subscribe [:data/market-order]))
  (rf/dispatch [:ws/send {:event      :data/cg-data
                          :on-success #(println :success %)
                          :on-failure #(println :failure %)}])
  )
